rComments: A lot of content to know in the lecture slides which were not explained thoroughly. Exam review was difficult because it was not specified what was needed to know. A lot of additional readings in addition to textbook readings. This course was content heavy, be ready for a lot of work and self teaching.
Exams are hard 50 definition, 10 essay questions. Personally, I avoid taking her classes just cause of the exam.
